\" \n    onclick=\"loadEarlierLogs()\">\n    Load earlier (<span id=\"load-earlier-count\">0</span> more lines)\n</button>\n```\n\n**Visibility logic:**\n- Button initially hidden\n- Becomes visible when SSE meta event is received with `skipped > 0`\n- Updates count dynamically as user loads more lines\n\n**JavaScript Implementation (lines 305-349):**\n- `loadEarlierLogs()` function fetches from `/api/runs/{id}/logs?end={skippedLines}&limit=1000`\n- Creates document fragments for better performance\n- Inserts loaded lines at top of log viewer (preserving scroll position)\n- Updates `skippedLines` tracker from response\n- Hides button when all earlier lines are loaded (`skippedLines = 0`)\n\n**Scroll Preservation Logic (lines 327-330):**\n```javascript\nvar prevScrollHeight = logViewer.scrollHeight;\nlogContent.insertBefore(fragment, logContent.firstChild);\nlogViewer.scrollTop += logViewer.scrollHeight - prevScrollHeight;\n```\n\n### 5. **SSE Meta Event Handling**\n\n**File:** `/workspace/internal/adapters/web/templates/run_detail.html` (lines 158-167)\n\nThe template registers a listener for the \"meta\" SSE event:\n```javascript\nsource.addEventListener('meta', function(e) {\n    var meta = JSON.parse(e.data);\n    skippedLines = meta.skipped || 0;\n    if (skippedLines > 0) {\n        loadEarlierCount.textContent = skippedLines;\n        loadEarlierBtn.style.display = '';\n    }\n});\n```\n\n### 6. **Log Filtering and Parsing**\n\n**File:** `/workspace/internal/adapters/web/handler.go`\n\n**New helper function** (lines 1189-1212):\n- `readVisibleLogLines(logPath)` - reads full.log and returns parsed, filtered log lines\n- Filters out protocol-only LLM events (empty type)\n- Handles large JSON lines (up to 1MB with 256KB buffer)\n\n**Parsing logic:**\n- `parseFullLogLine` - parses `[timestamp] [type] content` format\n- `parseLLMLogLine` - extracts human-readable text from Claude JSON\n\n### 7. **CSS Styling**\n\n**File:** `/workspace/internal/adapters/web/static/style.css` (lines 407-423)\n\nNew `.load-earlier-btn` styles:\n```css\n.load-earlier-btn {\n    display: block;\n    width: 100%;\n    padding: 0.4rem;\n    background: var(--bg-secondary);\n    border: none;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);\n    cursor: pointer;\n    color: var(--link);\n}\n.load-earlier-btn:hover { background: var(--border); }\n.load-earlier-btn:disabled { opacity: 0.5; cursor: wait; }\n```\n\n### 8. **Test Coverage**\n\n**File:** `/workspace/internal/adapters/web/handler_stream_test.go`\n\nNew comprehensive tests added:\n- `TestSSE_CompletedRun_TailsLast1000` - verifies 1000-line limit with meta event\n- `TestSSE_CompletedRun_NoMetaWhenUnderLimit` - verifies no meta event when under 1000 lines\n- `TestAPILogs_Pagination` - tests pagination endpoint with default limit\n- `TestAPILogs_PaginateEarlier` - tests loading earlier pages\n- `TestAPILogs_FirstPage` - tests first page clamping\n- `TestAPILogs_RunNotFound` - tests error handling\n- `TestAPILogs_NoLogFile` - tests empty log handling\n- Helper function `writeNLogLines` - generates test log files\n\n### Key Files Modified:\n\n1. **`/workspace/internal/adapters/web/handler.go`** - Main handler implementation\n2. **`/workspace/internal/adapters/web/templates/run_detail.html`** - UI template and JavaScript\n3. **`/workspace/internal/adapters/web/static/style.css`** - Styling for load button\n4. **`/workspace/internal/adapters/web/handler_stream_test.go`** - Test coverage for new features\n\n### Architecture Overview:\n\n```\nCompleted Run (large logs)\n    ↓\nSSE /stream endpoint\n    ↓\nTail 1000 lines + meta event → Browser\n    ↓\nDisplay 1000 lines + \"Load earlier\" button\n    ↓\nUser clicks button\n    ↓\nFetch /api/logs?end=X&limit=1000\n    ↓\nInsert at top, preserve scroll position\n    ↓\nUpdate button count or hide if all loaded\n```"}],"totalDurationMs":40227,"totalTokens":60507,"totalToolUseCount":20,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2619,"cache_read_